SUMMARY:Tiny Tappers: Ages 3-5
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260316T164500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260316T173000
UID:251206hOY6zoBwlUm74qWiwm2CSQ
DESCRIPTION:Mondays\, January 26 – March 16\, 2026 4:45 PM – 5:30 PM N
 o class Monday\, February 16\n\nRecital Date\n\nSaturday\, March 21\, 2026
  Time TBA\n\nExperience Level\n\nBeginning and Intermediate\n\nEvent Categ
 ories: Dance & Movement\, Kids\n\nAge\\(s\\)\n\n3-5\n\n$165 Registration F
 ee\n\nRegistration Fee includes full enrollment for 7 weeks of instruction
  and the recital costume fee\n\nStep into the rhythm and fun with our Tiny
  Tappers class\, designed especially for young dancers aged 3 to 5 years!\
 n\nWhat you’ll Create\n\nStep into the rhythm and fun with our Tiny Tap
 pers class\, designed especially for young dancers aged 3 to 5 years! Thi
 s lively and engaging class introduces the basics of tap dance\, fostering
  rhythm\, coordination\, and confidence in a joyful environment. Through a
 ge-appropriate techniques\, rhythmic exercises\, and upbeat music\, childr
 en will learn foundational tap steps like shuffles\, toe taps\, heel digs 
 and more! Whether your child is a first-time dancer or loves to move to th
 e beat\, Tiny Tappers is the perfect way to develop musicality\, motor ski
 lls\, and a love for dance. Tap into the fun and watch your little one shi
 ne! No experience is necessary – just bring your tap shoes and a smile! 
 Recital on Saturday\, March 21st. More info on recital soon.\n\nRequired S
 upply List\n\nTap shoes of any color and style\, Comfortable clothing to 
 move in or dance-wear such as leotards\, skirts\, skirted leotards and ti
 ghts \\(with shoes\\) of any color or style. Please no tutus or pajamas in
  class. Hair pulled off face. Dress in layers as it can go from chilly to
  warm fast! Being dressed and ready for class is part of the experience an
 d encourages focus and participation. You can find tap shoes at Discount 
 Dance Supply \, Amazon\, Capezio\, and Bloch and sometimes Target for 
 Kid’s sizes. Any color and style will do. Not necessary for the first c
 lass\, may wear hard soled shoes.\n\nLocation
LOCATION:Sonoma Community Center
URL:https://sonomacommunitycenter.org/programs/tiny-tappers-ages-3-5/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
