 iate\n\nEvent Category: Ceramics\n\nAge\\(s\\)\n\n17\\+\n\n$265 – Regist
 ration Cost $30 – Materials Fee $295 – Total Registration Cost\n\nJoin
  visiting artist Ari Stein in this introduction to wheel thrown and decora
 ted ceramics.\n\nWhat you’ll do\n\nJoin Ari in this introduction to whee
 l thrown and decorated ceramics. We will spend half the class focusing on 
