DESCRIPTION:AHA BLS Certification Class \\(Blended Learning\\)\n\nBLS Blen
 ded Learning / BLS Skills Session\n\nAHA BLS certification course for heal
 thcare providers. Blended Learning consists of an online course followed b
 y an in-person Skills Session. This American Heart Association Basic Life 
 Support class includes skills testing of cardiac and respiratory arrest ma
 nagement\, CPR\, AED use\, and choking treatment for all ages.\n\nAmerican
  Heart Association BLS Provider certifications are issued on the same day.
 \n\nLearn from a top-rated\, local CPR training company with over 900 5-st
 ar reviews! Our classes are fun\, engaging\, and expertly taught by experi
 enced first responders.\n\nLEARN MORE and ENROLL: https://vivecpr.com/clas
 s/heartcode-bls/\n\nCONTACT US: \\(707\\) 612-3277
