BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://www.jewishnovato.com/templates/articlecco_cdo/aid/6748161/jewish/Jewpernatural.htm", "Press Democrat": "https://www.jewishnovato.com/templates/articlecco_cdo/aid/6748161/jewish/Jewpernatural.htm"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://www.jewishnovato.com/templates/articlecco_cdo/aid/6748161/jewish/Jewpernatural.htm"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Jewish Course in Novato Explores Dreams\, Astrology\, and the Evil
  Eye
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T204500
UID:260211_D1-jztMkkK6y_NAzimjlQ
DESCRIPTION:NOVATO\, CA — Chabad Jewish Center of Novato is launching a
  new fascinating 4 week class: Jewpernatural: Signs\, Spirits\, and Super
 stition in Jewish Belief\, a new four-week course from the beginning Mond
 ay\, February 24.\n\nThe course addresses questions many people are asking
  today: Do dreams have meaning? Is there such a thing as destiny? What doe
 s Judaism say about astrology and the “evil eye”? How does Jewish trad
 ition understand souls and the afterlife?\n\nDrawing on Talmud\, Jewish p
 hilosophy\, and Kabbalah\, Jewpernatural offers a grounded\, thoughtful ap
 proach to topics that often generate curiosity\, skepticism\, and uncertai
 nty.\n\nThe four sessions include:\n\nDreams & Direction\n\nStars & Signs\
 n\nJinx & The Evil Eye\n\nPara & Normal (souls\, angels\, spirits\, and t
 he afterlife)\n\n“People are curious about these topics\, but they also 
 want serious\, authentic answers\,” said Rabbi Menachem Landa of Chabad 
 Jewish Center of Novato. “This course helps participants separate myth f
 rom meaning and gain practical Jewish perspective for real life.”\n\nThe
  course is open to all\, regardless of background or prior Jewish learning
 .\n\nEvent Details What: Jewpernatural (4-weekcourse) When: Begins Monda
 y\, February 24 Where: Chabad Jewish Center of Novato Format: In person 
 and Zoom Registration: Jewishnovato.com/Jewpernatural Contact: info@Jewi
 shnovato.com
LOCATION:chabad Jewish center of Novato
URL:https://www.jewishnovato.com/templates/articlecco_cdo/aid/6748161/jewi
 sh/Jewpernatural.htm
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian, Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/bachata-with-alex/17285108/2026-03-17T19"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Bachata with ALEX
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T203000
UID:251213wzVW3-JlqUuyGuC3g2s9pA
DESCRIPTION:Bachata with ALEX\n\nReady to take your bachata to the next le
 vel?\n\nThis intermediate bachata class is for dancers who have already ma
 stered the basics and are ready for a new challenge. We’ll build on your
  foundation with a focus on more intricate footwork\, technique\, and part
 ner work.\n\nAdvanced turn patterns and combinations\n\nStyling and body m
 ovement to add flair to your dancing\n\nMusicality to connect with the rhy
 thm and emotion of the music\n\nFeeling comfortable with your basic bachat
 a steps and ready for more?\n\nOur intermediate bachata class is designe
 d for dancers who want to elevate their skills. We’ll move beyond the fu
 ndamentals to focus on more complex technique\, footwork\, and partner wo
 rk.\n\nThis class will help you:\n\nRefine your leading and following\n\nL
 earn combinations and techniques\n\nDevelop your personal style and musica
 lity\n\nIf you’re ready to add some fire to your dancing\, this is the c
 lass for you!\n\nImportant Details\n\nBasic steps and turns required. We
 ’ll be moving into combinations\, so a solid grasp of your basic steps i
 s essential.\n\nNo partner necessary: Come solo or bring a friend—eithe
 r way\, you’ll have plenty of opportunities to dance.\n\nPlease wear non
 -marking shoe soles: This helps us keep our dance floor in great condition
 .\n\nCome join us and discover the joy of bachata! We can’t wait to see 
 you on the dance floor.
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/bachata-with-alex/17285
 108/2026-03-17T19
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
