DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260318T133000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260318T153000
UID:260201dXvFbWVQKUuPJGfNHoeuew
DESCRIPTION:What is a digital story? A digital story is a narrated slidesh
 ow or movie that you voice over with your own personal story or poem. Brin
 g a flash drive or email yourself 10-20 photos\, or up to 5 short videos\,
  that you would like to include in your story. If you can't decide or aren
 't ready to share\, we will have some images available to get you started.
  Consider attending the iMovie Editing class to get a head start on your p
 roject. This class can be repeated multiple times. Advanced registration e
 ncouraged\, but not required. Maximum of 8 participants.
LOCATION:Central Santa Rosa Library
URL:https://events.sonomalibrary.org/event/create-digital-story-102331
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
