DESCRIPTION:The Vallejo JFK Library offers the Lawyers in the Library prog
 ramon the first and third Wednesdays of every month. Each meeting is 15 mi
 nutes. Space is limited and slots fill up on a first come\, first serve ba
 sis. Please callor come in-person to Vallejo JFK Library at 9am on the day
  of the program to reserve a spot. Currently\, our program offers phone co
 nsultations with a lawyer. If you have an appointment\, the attorney will 
 call you that evening between 5:30 - 7:15pm. PLEASE NOTE: In-person meetin
 gs are not currently offered. Coming to the library during the scheduled a
 ppointment window will not result in an in-person meeting. You will need a
  working phone to receive the call. The library is unable to provide telep
 hone access for a lawyer consultation. If you would like more information\
 , please call us at \\(866\\) 572-7587.
LOCATION:Vallejo John F. Kennedy Library
URL:https://solanolibrary.libnet.info/event/15399260
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
