X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Press Democrat": "https://mynorthbaytickets.com/e/napa-center-for-thought-culture-presents-chris-sch/tickets"}
X-SOURCE-ID:pressdemocrat
SUMMARY:A Night with National Geographic Urban Ecologist Dr. Chris Schell
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260320T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260320T193000
UID:260217L_VZ75Y_d0amqRAvWgXieg
DESCRIPTION:**A Night with National Geographic Urban Ecologist Dr. Chris S
 chell**\n\n**Friday\, March 20**\n\n**EcoLab Theater at CIA Copia\, Napa C
 A**\n\n**Doors: 5:30 PM | Program 6:00 PM**\n\nThink wildlife lives “som
 ewhere else”? Think again. Join National Geographic Explorer Dr. Chris S
 chell for a mind-expanding journey into the surprising world of urban coyo
 tes\, foxes\, raccoons — and the hidden histories that shaped the ecosys
 tems right outside our doors.\n\nDr. Schell’s groundbreaking work uncove
 rs how environmental injustice\, resilience\, and human choices ripple thr
 ough entire cities\, transforming the animals who live alongside us. You
 ’ll never see a neighborhood stroll the same way again.\n\nA powerful\, 
 eye-opening evening for anyone curious about science\, justice\, and the w
 ild stories unfolding in our own backyard.\n\n**Be curious.  Be surprised
 .  Be there.**
LOCATION:EcoLab Theater at CIA Napa
URL:https://mynorthbaytickets.com/e/napa-center-for-thought-culture-presen
 ts-chris-sch/tickets
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
