DESCRIPTION:Volunteer on the farm on Saturdays\, 9am-noon.\n\nSign up for a
  spot at https://calendly.com/petalumabounty\n\nTasks typically include we
 eding\, seeding\, mulching\, planting\, and when it's the season\, harvest
 ing. It's a great way to get out and help grow fresh\, healthy food for th
 e community.
