DESCRIPTION:California wants undocumented families to have bright futures\
 , and college is a great way to make that happen!  California believes in 
 us. All of us. Whether or not we have papers\, this state wants us learnin
 g\, growing and building skills that matter\, skills we can use\, with or 
 without a Security Number.  &#160\;  SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream C
 enter invites you to join these virtual professional development series de
 signed for those who work with undocumented students.Register here! (https
 ://events.zoom.us/ev/ApPBLph87f5_luSan-vCvSjbPLKtmvh1KgOjUdbd-bxlxiDLPMRt~
 AhrWN6KvTF36P9vCuV-ylaFaiNvrVDSaQ5-Do8DGVzZHuRCWff4dGVBn2g)  For more info
 rmation\, visit the SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Center Website (ht
 tps://dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-events-2025-2026)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T194930Z
