 o have bright futures\, and college is a great way to make that happen!</p
 ><p>  California believes in us. All of us. Whether or not we have papers\
 , this state wants us learning\, growing and building skills that matter\,
  skills we can use\, with or without a Security Number.</p><p>  &#160\;</p
 ><p>  SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Center invites you to join these
  virtual professional development series designed for those who work with 
 undocumented students.</p><p><a href="https://events.zoom.us/ev/ApPBLph87f
 5_luSan-vCvSjbPLKtmvh1KgOjUdbd-bxlxiDLPMRt~AhrWN6KvTF36P9vCuV-ylaFaiNvrVDS
