DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260322T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260322T160000
SUMMARY:English Country Dance Napa
DESCRIPTION:North Bay Contra Dance\nEnglish country dancing is done in lon
 g lines (like contra)\, circles\, or in geometric sets (squares\, triangle
 s). Like our contra dances\, there is live music and a caller. You can com
 e by yourself or with friends\, since we change partners after each dance.
  If you’ve ever done contra or square dancing\, much of our dance vocabu
 lary will be familiar to you since both of those styles evolved from Engli
 sh country dancing.\n\nThe dance is held the 1st and 3rd Sundays of each m
 onth\, 2-4:30 pm\, to live music\, all levels of experience welcome\; and 
 occasional 5th Sundays for Advanced dancers. Admission is $15 for members 
 of NBCDS and its affiliates\, $8 for young adults ages 19-30\, and $3 for 
 youth ages 6 – 18.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-bay-contra-dance/events/3132693
 71/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260208T204436Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260208T204436Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
