SUMMARY:Beginners in The Work of Byron Katie: Newcomers Welcome
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\nA free Zoom meditation session design
 ed with newcomers in mind. Sessions will include at least one hour of faci
 litation (meditation) and there is room for questions and answers througho
 ut. If you're curious about The Work\, you're invited to join!\n\nSee you 
 there!\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no members have join
 ed after 10 minutes.\n\n**To book a free introductory private session with
  Emrys\, [click here](https://calendly.com/mindfulnesswithemrys/onehourses
 sion)[.](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)**\n\nEmrys also orga
 nises a free Work of Byron Katie Meetup group. Visit: [https://www.meetup.
 com/thework-runsfree](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/)\n\n*Find o
 ut more about Emrys [here](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)[.]
 (http://linktr.ee/theworkrunsfree)*
