UID:event_312814190@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260317T163302Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260401T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260401T200000
SUMMARY:UPDATE: 1st Wednesday! Wednesday Night Walk start at STARBUCKS  on
  the East Side
DESCRIPTION:"SONOMA COUNTY OUTDOORS"\nWednesday Night Walk: Petaluma East 
 Side Green Belt\n\n* Want to walk for fitness and exercise?\n* New to walk
 ing and want to build up stamina?\n* Like a slower pace than our Tuesday N
 ight Fitness Hike?\n* Would walking with a committed group of walkers help
  you?\n\nIf you said yes to any of these\, then the Wednesday Night Walk i
 n Petaluma is for you. We start at STARBUCKS at the leghorn shopping cente
 r\, and walk about 4-1/2 miles depending on weather conditions and the pac
 e of the group that night.\n\nDETAILS:\n\n* Meetup time: 6:00pm (we walk a
 t 6:10 sharp)\n* Meetup location: STARBUCKS\n* Distance: \\~ 4.5 miles\n* 
 Duration: 75-80 minutes\n* Pace: Easy/Moderate (about 2.5-3 mph or 20-24 m
 inute miles)\n* Difficulty: Easy (if you've walked 3-4 miles recently)\n* 
 Hills: Mostly flat\n* Optional After-walk gathering at\n* WHAT TO BRING:\n
 * A good pair of walking shoes\n* Water (you'll be glad you did)\n* A fun 
 attitude!\n\nSO HOW FAST ARE WE WALKING?\nThe Wednesday Night Walk is abou
 t 2.5 - 3 mph (20-24 minute miles)\nThe Tuesday Night Fitness Hike is abou
 t 3.5-4 mph (15-17 minute miles)\n\nHOW DO YOU PARTICIPATE?\nSign up with 
 Meetup and RSVP Today! This also gets you on our email list to make you aw
 are of upcoming events\, hikes and walks. You will not be spammed. If you 
 are\, let me know. Spamming will not be tolerated.\n\nWHY DO YOU NEED TO R
 SVP?\nIt's important to RSVP for these walks. When all the people have arr
 ived for a walk that have RSVP'd\, we leave... it might mean we leave earl
 y. If you didn't RSVP we are not going to wait for you. Plus\, it's just a
  nice courtesy to the organizer and other participants. Please take the ti
 me to RSVP.\n\nQUESTIONS?\nEmail me with any questions by using the "Conta
 ct Us" link on the left hand side bar of this meetup group page.\n\nHope t
 o see you on a walk or hike soon!\n\nGary\nSCO Organizer
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-county-outdoors/events/3128141
 90/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260110T045215Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260110T045215Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
