DESCRIPTION:SRJC students have the opportunity to spend July 5–26\, 2026
  studying yoga and wellness in beautiful Costa Rica while earning 6 units 
 of college credit.  The program includes yoga training\, cultural experien
 ces\, and exciting excursions such as visits to Manuel Antonio National Pa
 rk\, Monteverde Cloud Forest\, and Indigenous communities.  For more infor
 mation\, visit SRJC's Study Abroad website! (https://study-abroad.santaros
 a.edu/costa-rica-summer-2026-information)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T225754Z
