 summer-2026
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  SRJC students have the opportunity to sp
 end July 5–26\, 2026 studying yoga and wellness in beautiful Costa Rica 
 while earning 6 units of college credit.</p><p>  The program includes yoga
  training\, cultural experiences\, and exciting excursions such as visits 
 to Manuel Antonio National Park\, Monteverde Cloud Forest\, and Indigenous
  communities.</p><p>  For more information\, visit <a href="https://study-
