  textiles and sculpture. Join us in the Museum on Friday\, April 3rd for a
  casual reception. Meet the artists and enjoy a light snack.  For more inf
 ormation\, visit SRJC's Multicultural Museum Website! (https://museum.sant
 arosa.edu/event/honoring-ancestry)
