 _Brian_Antonson_2019_11_TC_edit_002.rev.1772833103.jpg
CATEGORIES:Arts,Department Events,District Events
DESCRIPTION:The Sonoma County Student Film Festival was initiated 18 years
  ago by the Student Government President\, Amanda Swan\, and launched at S
 RJC Petaluma. The Sonoma County Film Festival (SCSFF) encourages students 
 to build academic and professional connections with their peers and commun
 ity. The goal of the event is to connect and introduce student filmmakers 
 within the community to our own Film &amp\; Media Arts programs here at SR
 JC\, other filmmakers and film and media opportunities in the area.  For m
 ore information\, visit the Sonoma County Student Film website! (https://s
 tudentlife.santarosa.edu/sonoma-county-student-film-festival)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T214140Z
LOCATION:Ellis Auditorium - Petaluma Campus
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/16285-sonoma-county-student-film-
 festival
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The Sonoma County Student Film Festival 
 was initiated 18 years ago by the Student Government President\, Amanda Sw
 an\, and launched at SRJC Petaluma. The Sonoma County Film Festival (SCSFF
 ) encourages students to build academic and professional connections with 
 their peers and community. The goal of the event is to connect and introdu
 ce student filmmakers within the community to our own Film &amp\; Media Ar
 ts programs here at SRJC\, other filmmakers and film and media opportuniti
 es in the area.</p><p>  For more information\, visit the <a href="https://
 studentlife.santarosa.edu/sonoma-county-student-film-festival" target="_bl
 ank" rel="noopener">Sonoma County Student Film website!</a></p>
