 he SRJC Disability Cultural Center. This is a welcoming space for disabled
  students and allies to connect\, share experiences\, ask questions\, and 
 build community.&#160\;</p><p>  Whether you're looking for peer support\, 
 conversation\, or just a place to be among others who understand\, you're 
 invited to stop by and be part of the DCC community.</p><p><strong>The DCC
  is on the third-floor landing in the Bertolini Student Center.</strong></
 p><p>  For any additional access needs or questions\, please send us an em
 ail at <a href="mailto:srjcdcc@santarosa.edu">srjcdcc@santarosa.edu</a>&#1
 60\;</p><p>  Visit the <a href="https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc" target="_bl
 ank" rel="noopener">DRD website here!</a></p>
