LOCATION:Burbank Auditorium Main Stage Theatre - Santa Rosa Campus
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/10071-hello-dolly-the-musical-bar
 gain-show
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  This musical adaptation of Thornton Wild
 er's hit play <em>The Matchmaker</em> includes humor\, romance\, energetic
  dance\, and some of the greatest songs in music theatre history.<br />  T
 he romantic and comic exploits of Dolly Gallagher Levi\, turn-of-the-centu
 ry matchmaker and "woman who arranges things\," are a thrill and highly en
 tertaining to audiences.</p><p>  Directed by Gina Alvarado<br />  Book by 
 Michael Stewart<br />  Music and Lyrics by Jerry Herman</p><p>  &#160\;</p
 ><p>  Location: Main Stage Theatre at Burbank Auditorium on Santa Rosa Cam
 pus.</p><p>  Tickets: $15</p><p>  &#160\;</p><p><a href="https://srjc.univ
 ersitytickets.com/w/event.aspx?id=1783" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buy
  tickets here!</a></p><p>  SRJC Theatre Arts Website: <a href="https://the
 atrearts.santarosa.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://theatreart
 s.santarosa.edu/</a>&#160\;</p>
