 9249.jpg
CATEGORIES:Department Events
DESCRIPTION:Undocumented Californians are building businesses\, and everyo
 ne can learn from their effort. Whether you have papers or not. Whether yo
 u want to launch something one day or support a friend who does. This sess
 ion invites new ways of thinking about work\, creativity\, and contributio
 n that helps neighbors. We'll look at entrepreneurial paths that make room
  for people who don't see themselves in grind culture\, and for those who 
 want to build something meaningful\, sustainable\, and rooted in purpose. 
  &#160\;  SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Center invites you to join t
 hese virtual professional development series designed for those who work w
 ith undocumented students.Register here! (https://events.zoom.us/ev/An2mq_
 9p0JQpRAYki5BLgRh9wjPS4D6XnMxqZEl2F3lcZU-z2nHz~AnlWoDIvcvd7J558i96u7TtP3SK
 eaUn8DtpFAZ1N2r67C0mC28hPlTz9iQ)  For more information\, visit the SRJC Un
 docu • Immigrant • Dream Center Website (https://dream.santarosa.edu/w
 orkshops-events-2025-2026)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T210954Z
LOCATION:Zoom
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/15543-light-the-dream-business-ma
 king-101
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Undocumented Californians are building b
 usinesses\, and everyone can learn from their effort. Whether you have pap
 ers or not. Whether you want to launch something one day or support a frie
 nd who does. This session invites new ways of thinking about work\, creati
 vity\, and contribution that helps neighbors. We'll look at entrepreneuria
 l paths that make room for people who don't see themselves in grind cultur
 e\, and for those who want to build something meaningful\, sustainable\, a
 nd rooted in purpose.</p><p>  &#160\;</p><p>  SRJC Undocu • Immigrant 
 • Dream Center invites you to join these virtual professional developmen
 t series designed for those who work with undocumented students.</p><p><a 
 href="https://events.zoom.us/ev/An2mq_9p0JQpRAYki5BLgRh9wjPS4D6XnMxqZEl2F3
 lcZU-z2nHz~AnlWoDIvcvd7J558i96u7TtP3SKeaUn8DtpFAZ1N2r67C0mC28hPlTz9iQ" tar
 get="_blank" rel="noopener">Register here!</a></p><p>  For more informatio
 n\, visit the <a href="https://dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-events-2025-2
 026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Ce
 nter Website</a></p>
