SUMMARY: Mother's Day Self Care Retreat
DESCRIPTION:Overview\n\nCelebrate Mother’s Day with a rejuvenating self-c
 are experience—pamper\, relax\, and glow alongside the women you love.\n\
 nJoin us at Allume Med Spa for our Allume Facial Event\, a Mother’s Day–i
 nspired self-care experience designed to honor and celebrate moms\, careg
 ivers\, and the special women in your life.\n\nThis event is the perfect 
 opportunity to treat yourself—or bring your mother\, daughter\, sister\, 
 or friend—for a shared day of relaxation\, rejuvenation\, and radiant ski
 n. Spend quality time together while enjoying a series of indulgent treat
 ments in a calm\, spa-like environment.\n\n\nEvent Pricing:\n\n  * $199 f
 or two people\n  * $119 for one person (single bookings must call to sche
 dule)\n\nImportant scheduling note:\nThis is a timed experience. The even
 t runs from 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM\, and each guest will select an individual 
 treatment time within that window.\nAfter purchasing your ticket\, please
  call Allume Med Spa to reserve your preferred time slot.\nSingle-person 
 bookings are scheduled by phone only.\n\n\nYour Allume facial experience 
 includes:\n\n  * 30-Minute Glow Facial customized to refresh and illumina
 te your skin\n  * LED Light Therapy to promote healing and enhance radian
 ce\n  * Chair Massage for deep relaxation\n  * Lymphatic Drainage to redu
 ce puffiness and support detoxification\n  * Cervical Neck Care to releas
 e tension and improve circulation\n  * Sound Bath Immersion for full-body
  relaxation\n  * Essential Oil Aromatherapy to enhance your sensory exper
 ience\n  * Paraffin Hand Treatment to deeply hydrate and soften skin\n  *
  Spa Refreshments to enjoy while you unwind\n\nMake this Mother’s Day spe
 cial by gifting yourself—or a loved one—a restorative and luxurious self-
 care experience at Allume. Celebrate the women in your life with glowing 
 skin\, calm energy\, and shared moments of wellness.\n\n✨ Limited availab
 ility. Advance registration and phone scheduling required.
CATEGORIES:spa,selfcare,mothersday,retreat
