X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Santa Rosa Junior College": "https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/15549-lessons-from-the-dream-movement"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Santa Rosa Junior College": "https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/15545-lessons-from-the-dream-movement"}
X-SOURCE-ID:calendar_livewhale
SUMMARY:Lessons From The Dream Movement
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260512T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260512T123000
DTSTAMP:20260227T131534Z
UID:20260512T180000Z-15545@calendar.santarosa.edu
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260512T110000
ATTACH:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/live/image/gid/3/width/80/height/80/
 crop/1/src_region/0,0,800,800/288_Dream_Center_Services_2024__1.rev.174136
 9249.jpg
CATEGORIES:Department Events
DESCRIPTION:Using the past\, to inform the present\, to shape the future. 
  From Dream Clubs in local colleges to a national movement\, undocumented 
 youth turned isolation into community and community into power. Whether yo
 u're into history\, social movements\, or you're simply curious about how 
 a disenfranchised community built national influence\, this conversation i
 s for you!Register here! (https://events.zoom.us/ev/Ari35dd7sJIXd1xyPWqFl8
 TB6Y-YQK7kmCwVt4RVvIF1H-qxG3hS~AnvT0N5dg7dUYGAFFZGL1RJZwCmuHCNaOQ_hA4u2EAc
 twtE3JnWx7OxGXg)  For more information\, visit the SRJC Undocu • Immigra
 nt • Dream Center Website (https://dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-events-
 2025-2026)
