LOCATION:Zoom
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/15545-lessons-from-the-dream-move
 ment
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Using the past\, to inform the present\,
  to shape the future.</p><p>  From Dream Clubs in local colleges to a nati
 onal movement\, undocumented youth turned isolation into community and com
 munity into power. Whether you're into history\, social movements\, or you
 're simply curious about how a disenfranchised community built national in
 fluence\, this conversation is for you!</p><p><a href="https://events.zoom
 .us/ev/Ari35dd7sJIXd1xyPWqFl8TB6Y-YQK7kmCwVt4RVvIF1H-qxG3hS~AnvT0N5dg7dUYG
