 r">Register here!</a></p><p>  For more information\, visit the <a href="ht
 tps://dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-events-2025-2026" target="_blank" rel=
 "noopener">SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Center Website</a></p>
