SUMMARY:The North Bay Get Down (Free Monthly Funk Jam Night)
DESCRIPTION:THE BEST MONDAY NIGHT IN THE NORTH BAY! 3rd Monday Each Month (June 2026 is an exception). This is a live monthly funk jam and dance party for musicians and music lovers of all kinds! Each month features a DJ\, then a rotating “House Band” of the top musicians\, followed by a Special Guest Artist\, then a curated/open funk jam – all music is improvised on the spot for a wild\, spontaneous dance party. Great live music\, dancing\, drinks\, and community vibes. Hosted by Ethan Schiff! \n6:30pm: Doors Open + Live DJ Begins\n7:15: House Band Jam\n8pm: Special Guest Artist\n8:30 – 10:30pm: Curated/Open Jam \n*3rd Monday Every Month — Upcoming: July 20\, Aug 17\n*Follow @NorthBayGetDown on Instagram for real-time updates
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/the-north-bay-get-down-free-monthly-funk-jam-night-3/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
CATEGORIES:Funk
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Socials.png
END:VEVENT
