SUMMARY: Halloween Trick or Treat Trail
DESCRIPTION:A time of Bats and Broomsticks\, Blood and Bugs - and of cour
 se\, Downtown Petaluma’s Safe “Trick or Treat Trail” with the downtown Me
 rchants!\n\nParents - gather your little ghosts\, goblins\, monsters\, Ha
 rry Potters\, witches on broomsticks\, and princesses\, and join the part
 icipating downtown merchants for the Annual Trick or Treat Trail this Hal
 loween\, Saturday\, October 31 ~ from 3pm-5:30pm!\n\n\nDownload the Trick
  or Treat Trail Map for a list of participating locations on Kentucky St\
 , 4th St\, Western Ave\, Petaluma Blvd\, 2nd St\, “C” St\, Theater Distri
 ct\, and the River Plaza Shopping Center. Participating businesses will b
 e handing out Halloween goodies to costumed children!\n\n\nParticipating 
 merchants will have signage placed outside their stores and noted on the 
 map.\nThe Trick or Treat Trail Map will be available the week of the even
 t on this page\, or pick up from the Petaluma Visitors Center (hours on V
 isitPetaluma.com http://visitpetaluma.com/?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAYnJpZ
 BExYm5jemp6a0NVNXdIZVVvcXNydGMGYXBwX2lkEDIyMjAzOTE3ODgyMDA4OTIAAR62NbH49I
