DESCRIPTION:Brain teasers\, corset squeezers\, delicious pizza\, and cock
 tails too!\n\nGriffo's monthly DRAG TRIVIA is in full swing so reserve yo
 ur spot today! Our fabulous host Adda Boob will keep your brain spry and 
 your eyes tantalized the Griffo team serves up our delicious rotating lib
 ations ! Grab a bite from Pizza 909 and give your brain a workout! Trivia
  Night never tasted so good!\n\nWho's Hosting: Adda Boob\n\nWho's Cooking
 : Pizza 909\n\nWhen: Last Wednesday of EVERY month\, Doors @ 6pm - Trivia
  @ 7pm\n\nWhere: Griffo Distillery & Tasting Bar\n\nThis is a FREE all ag
 es event. RSVP's are encouraged because space is limited. Any minors must
  be accompanied by an adult.\n\n
